description: Ribeye and Ribeye Marrow are reminiscent of a cartoon tattoo style of lettering, but exhibit a playfulness that breaks traditional weight distribution across its letterforms. An edgy attitude, friendly syncopation, and highly legible letterforms makes these fonts a real pair of charmers.
